{"tid":1597621,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"【逆權●小店】ViuTv主持餐廳開業三個月勁蝕70萬 藉「5蚊兄弟飯」轉虧為盈大翻生","createTime":"2019-09-27T04:35:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T14:56:04.000Z","uid":525,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"94108a37568caec1c7c9d602a09a31eca14ff84c","tid":1597621,"uid":525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:35:17.000Z","msg":"彭嘉桓Moley本於ViuTv擔當節目助理，由於在職期間曾參加電視店節目「全民造星」因而被觀眾認識，未久又成功擔當清談節目主持。不過由於薪金微薄，三個月前與朋友一同於中環開設餐廳，幾位年輕人本來帶着雄心壯志，打算於飲食業創一番事業；豈料逆權運動爆出，令生意大失預算，3個月一度蝕本70萬，無糧出之餘，本月初更要向朋友借錢繳交5萬元舖租。在嚴峻情況下，Moley卻沒有結業的想法，「我唔可以俾藍絲睇死，再加上我哋已經『黃晒』，輸咗就會好柒！」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20190927/60087087\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190927%2F60087087&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYpLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=10f285aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190927%2F60087087&h=5bdcbfd2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20190927/60087087</a><br />\n有時間就去支持下"},{"pid":"3d5dd65221b356eea9d9153e3865f7ded9a2fbf2","tid":1597621,"uid":525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T05:29:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba0727acec0fec242731cb9717d899dc55ebdeaf","tid":1597621,"uid":282744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T08:27:47.000Z","msg":"viu tv啲員工大部份都黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b66807f83874e5af1dc2bc4fbe4326514037a97","tid":1597621,"uid":525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba0727acec0fec242731cb9717d899dc55ebdeaf","tid":1597621,"uid":282744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T08:27:47.000Z","msg":"viu tv啲員工大部份都黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" clas